Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your usual again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you remember it already, Robby?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hamburger with extra cheese...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lots of ketchup, and thick tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you if you put pickles on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Chinese or Vietnamese person...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been sniffing around about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That customer has been in here a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was asking me who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not Chinese or Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he's a brain surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With excellent skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the former fianc{\fnMeiryo U}é{\fnNarkisim} of a\Nhospital director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to make Eva do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too familiar with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan on playing the fianc{\fnMeiryo U}é{\fnNarkisim}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not only aren't you a doctor anymore,\Nbut you're a fugitive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to where you belong and fix yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be released someday,\Nif you're an exemplary inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not holding her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's going to parties every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess up my diner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hanging around here. Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.56,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(340,0)\pos(360,340)}The Man Who Saw The Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You met Kenzou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought I should let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you didn't punch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're done with today's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just today's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you took her to the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're having your dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the food served at parties\Nor high-class restaurants...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the hamburgers here are much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that's a compliment or an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're persistent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get hurt again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you get it when I told you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dangerous doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you work for The Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the one who ordered you to look after Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was someone even higher in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you the order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man that wears glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he forcing Eva to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only making her appear at parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She drinks, eats, and then goes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva must be doing something special there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman pointed at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pointed at someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a blond...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,young man with a pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all she did, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Eva right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's having dinner with my glasses-wearing boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva's job is probably over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I've finished this job...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll surely be killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The party's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Eva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent her back to her hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided not to carry a gun with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party was going normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fragrance of perfumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaningless laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva pointed at a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the glasses guy appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing with him another well-dressed young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the two young men...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shook hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice it at the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it appears that with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva's job was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who's assigned to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alcohol is starting to kick in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't have anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't shoot me in this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you shot your girlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stood in a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take me outside and shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else you'll have to pay for making the room all dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing left that I'm attached to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw me pointing at someone, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably did something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lured someone horrible to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lured Mephisto and Faust together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't have to attend parties anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have invitations for upcoming parties here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, after I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you fill in for me and see what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you please finish me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've gotten the wrong idea or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did we become that close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't kill people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you kill devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That suit and tie I bought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looks exactly like what Kenzou used to wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just dressing you up to look like Kenzou Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry up and kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I kill devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to sleep off this buzz a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you sleep in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Just leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always look grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone come looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the Japanese guy from last night left this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hellblau Hotel, room 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to contact him there if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get full on shitty hamburgers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lose my will to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get into anywhere with just one necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is he a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shook so many hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that his hand should have been swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he left the party hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth floor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But which room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have a seat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see him as well, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about something until he arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about the world coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid kept talking like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a child telling his parents all the fun things\Nthat happened at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was how he talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of the world coming to an end, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just some nonsense this crazy kid was spouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it an interesting story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy listening, Mr. Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been working for The Baby for three years now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you investigate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in prison before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eight years must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a model inmate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to get out of the place,\Neven though you committed murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was if fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman you killed, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was Edda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have poor taste, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a terrible drug addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried your best to get her off the drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something that's easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it love?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She cooked dinner and waited for you to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy life started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you want to get beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you saw a terrible sight when\Nyou returned to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her old boyfriend was in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was doing drugs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and mumbled something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kept repeating to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you shot and killed her, along with the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what was determined at the trial, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She killed herself, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attorney found gunpowder on her hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he deduced that she committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you still confessed to killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She begged you to kill her, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one who shot her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked your, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To shoot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She shot herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You deserted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you made her desire come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She froze to death when you were ten, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You deserted your mother back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised I was actually right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You carried your alcoholic mother home\Non your back every day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your mother kept telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you still carried your mother back every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left your mother there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning, you were told...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your mother froze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time, you thought to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only left her there because she asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both your mother and your drug-addicted\Ngirlfriend wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only let those who wanted to die, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't wrong. You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set them free from the misery of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva wants to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, the devil arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed by, making sure not to look at the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recited that to myself, like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:31.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.47,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:34.43,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
